Task 1

Question 1:
What does LAN stand for?

I literally didn't have to search this up, anyone who has played a cracked version of Minecraft in high school understands this term very well, since this was the only form-
-of multiplayer which meant you can only play with other students who are in your school and they are also using the same cracked client on their own computers.
I typed my answer "Local Area Network" and not surprisingly, I was correct.

